snippet.title: Pine Hearts Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Pine Hearts Caravan Park! 🌲
Coming to PC and Nintendo Switch May 23rd!
Wishlist now: 
https://www.nintendo.com/en-gb/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/Pine-Hearts-2563864.html
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1781010/Pine_Hearts/

--

Hop into your hiking boots as you and Tyke explore the paths and rivers of this cosy little world. 
Rummage around the park and find handy tools that will help you on your journey as you fill out your trusty hillwalking journal. 
Rediscover memories of Tyke's time in the park many summers ago and uncover the heartfelt story of his childhood.

--

Follow along with Little Nook for updates:
https://www.twitter.com/LittleNookGames
https://www.instagram.com/littlenookpublishing/

#PineHearts #LittleNook #wholesomegames #gametrailers
